<L>__{interior clara's room caldwell house late afternoon}
<A>__{the door flies open. clara bursts in, closing the door in the same movement. her eyes swing to someone o.s. and she freezes to the spot.}
<B>__{on}
<A>__{miss martin, standing by the window, cold and threatening. she has not taken the time to remove her hat. after a moment's pause, she moves slowly toward clara. the camera pans with her into a two shot. clara, her back pressing harder and harder against the door, becomes more terrified at the other's approach. miss martin appraises the girl a short moment and now suddenly slaps her hard across the face. clara opens her mouth, about to scream, but even stifles this impulse under the cold stare of her aunt.}
